le=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fii1665702708857.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fii1665702708857.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fii1665702708857.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fii1665702708857\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Mouse Pointer Icon\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Type of image to use as a background or icon—<code class=\"ph codeph\">Glyph</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">File</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fii1665702708857__section_w1643ab1b5b1_w1644ab1b5_w1645ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">(None)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No image is used</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Glyph</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use the specified glyph.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">File</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fii1665702708857__table_d12962e1_d12963e1_d12964e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use the specified file.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fii1665702708857__section_hjm_44d_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d604154e145\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fii1665702708857__p_d109781e1_d109782e1_d109783e1\">This property defines the type of image to use as\n            the drag and drop icon. Specify the image to use in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Glyph</span> or\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Image File</span> property, as appropriate.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fii1665702708857__p_d109784e1_d109785e1_d109786e1\">If you specify a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Glyph</span>, it\n            is useful to use glyphs that have both primary and secondary images. If you use a glyph\n            that has no secondary image, the cursor will be square and non-transparent.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fii1665702708857__p_d109787e1_d109788e1_d109789e1\">If you want the cursor to be non-rectangular (for\n            example an arrow), you should define a monochrome secondary glyph, in which white pixels\n            replace those where you want the cursor to be transparent.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fii1665702708857__section_x1z_p4d_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d604154e169\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fii1665702708857__ul_xy2_r4d_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fii1665702708857__li_d42599e1_d42600e1_d42601e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xzb1705583342348.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzb1705583342348.html\" title=\"Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets.\">Drag-and-Drop Formats</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbf1705582294349.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Glyphs</a><p>Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613023\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613023\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Mouse Pointer Icon Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Mouse Pointer Icon Type of image to use as a background or icon— Glyph or File . Value Description (None) No image is used Glyph Use the specified glyph. File Use the specified file. Description This property defines the type of image to use as the drag and drop icon. Specify the image to use in the Glyph or Image File property, as appropriate. If you specify a Glyph , it is useful to use glyphs that have both primary and secondary images. If you use a glyph that has no secondary image, the cursor will be square and non-transparent. If you want the cursor to be non-rectangular (for example an arrow), you should define a monochrome secondary glyph, in which white pixels replace those where you want the cursor to be transparent. Applies to Drag-and-Drop Formats Related Links Glyphs Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}